item.title: School Admin Panel
item.description: Fictitious School Admin PanelThe fifth individual project during Web-Development Fellowship at New York Code and Design Academy.It is a fullstack simple admin panel for a fictitious school whereby the administrator can create users and complete common administrative tasks.
